info: Dr. Alice Smith has been a practicing cardiologist for over a decade. She specializes in treating heart diseases and managing patients' cardiovascular health.
Dr. Bob Johnson is a highly experienced orthopedic surgeon known for his expertise in joint replacements and sports injuries.
Dr. Carol Davis is a renowned neurologist with a PhD in neuroscience. She has a keen interest in research and treatment of neurological disorders.
Dr. Daniel Wilson is a compassionate pediatrician dedicated to providing excellent care to children of all ages. He focuses on preventive care and healthy development.
Dr. Emma Brown is a skilled dermatologist with expertise in treating a wide range of skin conditions. She is also proficient in cosmetic dermatology.
Dr. Frank Green is a distinguished cardiothoracic surgeon with over 20 years of experience. He specializes in complex heart and lung surgeries.
